title: Joel Pollak, "Red November: Will the Country Vote Red for Trump Or Red for Socialism?"
description:
Breitbart News senior editor at large Joel Pollak discusses the 2020 democratic primaries and shares his thoughts on the 2020 election. He’s interviewed by Reason editor at large Matt Welch.
